title: FlowCode PIC V5.4
description:
Installation Procedure & activation
1-Start the installation by double-clicking on: FlowcodeV5-PICmicro.exe
2-Do not attempt to enterer a serial number (I think the demo choose option).
3 to 1 after the installation finish, run the program, a window appears asking you to enter the activation keys, starting from the activation flowcode two files:
FlowcodeV5 (PIC) _Activation_key.exe
FlowcodeV5 (PIC) _CD_key.exe
you will get a key and a key with a name of your choice (copy these information in the respective locations.
complete activation by copying the two (dll) of the same repectoire in the installation directory of flowcode 5
restart your application.

100% Working :) Enjoy your PIC Microcontroller Project with Simple Programming :) Technique.
